# Local secrets / overrides — NEVER commit real credentials.
# NOTE: config.php IS tracked on purpose as a PLACEHOLDER template (it ships only
# CHANGE_ME / empty values; the live server keeps its own real config.php, which
# deploy.yml preserves and never overwrites). Put real secrets ONLY on the server,
# never in a committed file. Use the patterns below for any local secret copies.
config.local.php
*.local.php
.env
.env.*

# Editor / OS cruft
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
*.swp
*~
